<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css" />
    <title>Climate Solutions</title>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen">
  <%- include('partials/navbar', {page: '/'}) %>

      <div class="container mx-auto">
      <div class="hero bg-base-200 min-h-32 rounded-lg p-10">
        <div class="hero-content text-center">
          <div class="max-w-md">
            <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">Welcome</h1>
            <p class="py-6">
                Browse our current collection of modern solutions to help fight Climate Change.
            </p>
            <a class="btn btn-primary"href = "/solutions/projects" >Get Started Now</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      </div>
      <div class="container mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
            <div class="card w-96 bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
                <figure>
                <img class="w-full" src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions/solution_farmlandrestoration01.jpg" alt="Abandoned Farmland Restoration" />
                </figure>
                <div class="card-body">
                <h2 class="card-title">Abandoned Farmland Restoration</h2>
                <p>Restoration can bring degraded farmland back into productivity and sequester carbon in the process.</p>
                <div class="card-actions justify-end">
                    <button class="btn btn-primary"><a href ="/solutions/projects/1">More Information</a></button>
                </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card w-96 bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
                <figure>
                <img class="w-full" src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions/solution_biomass01.jpg" alt="Biomass Power" />
                </figure>
                <div class="card-body">
                <h2 class="card-title">Biomass Power</h2>
                <p>Biomass feedstock can replace fossil fuels for generating heat and electricity. Perennial biomass offers a “bridge” to a clean, renewable energy future.</p>
                <div class="card-actions justify-end">
                    <button class="btn btn-primary"><a href ="/solutions/projects/4">More Information</a></button>
                </div>
                </div>
            </div>
                <div class="card w-96 bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
                    <figure>
                    <img class="w-full" src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions2020/solution_bicycle_infrastructure.jpg" alt="Bicycle Infrastructure" />
                    </figure>
                    <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title">Bicycle Infrastructure</h2>
                    <p>Infrastructure is essential for supporting safe and abundant bicycle use, which curbs emissions by reducing the need for fossil-fuel-dependent transportation.</p>
                    <div class="card-actions justify-end">
                        <button class="btn btn-primary"><a href ="/solutions/projects/3">More Information</a></button>
                    </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
        </div>
      </div>



    
</body>
</html>